---
import LegalLayout from '../layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
import { site } from '../data/site';
---
<LegalLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How ADVNTR Road handles email signups and site analytics."
  canonicalPath="/privacy"
>
  <p>
    ADVNTR Road collects the minimum information needed to run a small publication: your
    email address if you subscribe to the road list via Beehiiv, and basic, aggregated site
    analytics (see below). We do not sell your data.
  </p>
  <h2>Email</h2>
  <p>
    Email signups are processed by Beehiiv, our newsletter provider. Beehiiv's own privacy
    policy governs how your email address is stored and processed. You can unsubscribe from
    any email at any time.
  </p>
  <h2>Analytics</h2>
  <p>
    This site does not run third-party tracking by default at launch. If analytics are
    added later (see the launch report for provider options under consideration), this page
    will be updated to name the provider and what it collects.
  </p>
  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>Questions about this policy can be sent to <a href={`mailto:${site.contactEmail}`}>{site.contactEmail}</a>.</p>
  <p>This page is a launch draft, not final legal advice, and should be reviewed by Matt before relying on it.</p>
</LegalLayout>
